snippet.title: PTSD 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
PTSD guy returns in this all new epic adventure, full with completely new levels, secrets, weapons and more. PTSD guy's mental state is rapidly declining after the events of PTSD 1, and must travel on a big journey to find out what is causing this, and put an end to it.

The trailer doesn't do the mod Justice, go check it out for yourself!

Play PTSD 2 here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/the-ptsd-mod-2/downloads/ptsd-2

Music by Raxxo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fl2LMZH0tcU
